### Topaz API - Ingestion & Interoperability
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333

### ============================================
### Health Checks
### ============================================

### Health Check - Full status
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Readiness Probe (Kubernetes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready

### Liveness Probe (Kubernetes)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/live


### ============================================
### Flow A: Webhook Flash Ingest
### ============================================

### Webhook - Payment Gateway (Stripe)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/stripe
Content-Type: application/json
X-Webhook-Signature: sha256=abc123

{
    "id": "evt_123456",
    "type": "payment_intent.succeeded",
    "data": {
        "object": {
            "id": "pi_123456",
            "amount": 2000,
            "currency": "brl",
            "status": "succeeded"
        }
    }
}

### Webhook - Payment Gateway (PagSeguro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/pagseguro
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "notificationCode": "ABC123-DEF456",
    "notificationType": "transaction"
}

### Webhook - Marketing (Mailchimp)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/mailchimp
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "subscribe",
    "fired_at": "2024-01-15 10:30:00",
    "data": {
        "email": "user@example.com",
        "list_id": "abc123"
    }
}

### Webhook - CRM (HubSpot)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/hubspot
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "eventId": 1,
        "subscriptionId": 12345,
        "portalId": 67890,
        "occurredAt": 1704067200000,
        "eventType": "contact.creation",
        "objectId": 123
    }
]


### ============================================
### Flow B: CSV Batch Ingestion
### ============================================

### Upload CSV File
### Note: Replace the file path with your actual CSV file
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest/batch
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="data.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

id,name,email,amount
1,John Doe,john@example.com,100.50
2,Jane Smith,jane@example.com,250.00
3,Bob Wilson,bob@example.com,75.25
4,Alice Brown,alice@example.com,300.00
5,Charlie Davis,charlie@example.com,150.75
------FormBoundary--
